data.description:
Welcome to this meticulously maintained home nestled in the highly sought-after Ripple Creek Addition in Edmond, Oklahoma. This spacious 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom gem with a 2-car garage is situated on an appealing corner lot, boasting a host of upgrades that enhance its charm and functionality.

As you step inside, you'll be greeted by the warmth of a home that has been lovingly cared for. Recent upgrades include kitchen cabinet refacing, upgraded flooring, and a fresh coat of paint, ensuring a modern and inviting atmosphere. The thoughtful improvements extend to a new hot water heater and more, demonstrating a commitment to quality and comfort.

Beyond the impressive interior, the home creates a sense of spaciousness that defies its square footage. Each room is thoughtfully designed, contributing to an overall feeling of openness and comfort. The layout is perfect for both daily living and entertaining friends and family.

Convenience is key, and this home offers just that. Located in the heart of Edmond, it enjoys proximity to businesses, grocery stores, and retail shopping. Easy access to major highways, including the Broadway Extension and the Kilpatrick Turnpike, makes commuting a breeze.

The motivated seller is open to an interest rate buy down with an acceptable offer, making this an even more enticing opportunity for potential buyers. Don't miss your chance to experience the charm and convenience of this Edmond gem – schedule a showing today before this beauty is off the market!
